<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Forgot Password | CP Mail</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007bff, #00c6ff);
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .forgot-container {
      background: #fff;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 450px;
      margin: 5rem auto;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .forgot-container h2 {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #003366;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
    }

    .forgot-container p {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: #555;
    }

    .forgot-container input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0.8rem;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .forgot-container input:focus {
      border-color: #007bff;
      outline: none;
      box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(0,123,255,0.3);
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: #ffcc00;
      color: #003366;
      padding: 0.8rem;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: pointer;
      width: 100%;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: #e6b800;
    }

    .forgot-container a {
      color: #007bff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .forgot-container a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .forgot-container .footer-text {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #333;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="forgot-container">
    <h2>ลืมรหัสผ่าน</h2>
    <p>กรอกอีเมลของคุณเพื่อรับลิงก์สำหรับรีเซ็ตรหัสผ่าน</p>

    <form action="/forgot-password" method="POST">
      <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="กรอกอีเมล @kkumail.com" required>
      <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">ส่งลิงก์รีเซ็ต</button>
    </form>

    <p class="footer-text">จำรหัสผ่านได้แล้ว ? <a href="/login">เข้าสู่ระบบ</a></p>
  </div>

  
</body>
</html>